comments: Finnish entry in the Eurovision Song Contest 1963 in London. At the close of voting it had received the dreaded nul points placing 13th (equal last with the Netherlands' Annie Palmen with "Een speeldoos", Norway's Anita Thallaug with "Solvherv" and Sweden's Monica Zetterlund with En gång i Stockholm ) in a field of 16. This was Finland's first-ever nul points and last place.
